Enum Class GuiResEnum

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<GuiResEnum>
it.polimi.ingsw.am11.view.client.GUI.utils.GuiResEnum
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<GuiResEnum>, Constable
public enum GuiResEnum extends Enum<GuiResEnum>
This enum is used to map various resources used in the GUI to their file paths. Each enum value represents a different resource, and the associated String is the file path of the resource. The enum provides methods to get an enum value by a card ID, and to get the file path associated with an enum value.
